('21', 'Gyan Shakti Residential Schools of Excellence', '', 'Gyan Shakti Residential Schools of Excellence', 'Onfra ensures all campus visitors are verified through OTP and photo capture, all without hardware dependencies — making our school reception secure and future-ready.', '', '', 'Gyan Shakti Residential Schools of Excellence', 'https://onfra.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/ai-render-6915607-1.webp', 'Gyan Shakti Residential Schools of Excellence', '', 'Manual visitor verification causing security and tracking issues.\r\n,*Lack of accurate visitor detail collection and identity validation.\r\n,*No photo capture for visitor records.\r\n,*Need for a hardware-free solution to digitize the process.\r\n,*Requirement to ensure only genuine visitors enter the premises.', 'Onfra delivered a tailored, user-friendly digital visitor management system.\r\n,*Enabled accurate visitor detail collection and identity verification via OTP.\r\n,*Integrated photo capture for complete visitor records.\r\n,*Eliminated dependency on external hardware or complex infrastructure.\r\n,*Provided a secure, streamlined, and fully digitized visitor management experience.', 'Gyan Shakti Residential Schools of Excellence faced a critical challenge in managing their reception operations for external visitors. Their goal was to digitize the process of capturing and validating visitor information without relying on any external hardware. They needed a secure and efficient way to ensure only genuine visitors entered the premises — by collecting accurate details, verifying identity through OTP, and capturing photographs — all while maintaining a smooth and professional experience.,*\r\nOnfra stepped in to address these specific needs by designing a tailored, user-friendly digital solution. The platform enabled staff to seamlessly record and validate visitor information, including real-time OTP verification and photo capture, without the hassle of additional hardware setup. This ensured a secure, streamlined, and fully digitized visitor management experience that aligned perfectly with the operational values of Gyan Shakti Residential Schools.', 'Gyan Shakti Schools rely on Onfra’s powerful platform to create connected classrooms, streamlined staff collaboration, and secure access to resources that empower teachers and students alike.', 'Gyan Shakti Schools deployed Onfra to ensure safe campus access, student attendance monitoring, and seamless visitor tracking.', 'Educational Institution', 'Gujarat', '50', 'Visitor module', '1 year'),
('22', 'Easternbulk Lime Products Private Limited', '', 'Easternbulk Lime Products Private Limited', 'With Onfra, unauthorized access to our manufacturing unit is no longer a concern. Every visitor is verified, every entry is recorded, and compliance is seamless.', '', '', 'Easternbulk Lime Products Private Limited', 'https://onfra.io/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/ai-render-6916210-1.webp', 'Easternbulk Lime Products Private Limited', '', 'Unauthorized individuals entering manufacturing premises without proper validation.\r\n,*No centralized system to monitor, validate, and control visitor access.\r\n,*Difficulty distinguishing between authorized personnel, vendors, and unauthorized entrants.\r\n,*Lack of real-time monitoring and identity verification increasing security risks.\r\n,*Compliance concerns due to insufficient access control in sensitive manufacturing zones.', 'Onfra implemented a secure, hardware-independent visitor management system tailored for manufacturing environments.\r\n,*Digitized the entry process with OTP-based visitor verification and photo capture on arrival.\r\n,*Provided real-time visitor logs, automated approvals, and custom access controls to restrict access to specific zones.\r\n,*Delivered instant alerts for unauthorized entry attempts, strengthening security and compliance.\r\n,*Enabled full visibility and control over visitor movements, enhancing safety, operational integrity, and accountability across all manufacturing units.', 'Easternbulk, a leading name in manufacturing and logistics, faced a critical challenge in preventing unauthorized individuals from entering their high-security production units. With safety, compliance, and operational control at stake, they needed a solution that could verify every visitor without relying on complex hardware setups.,*\r\nOnfra stepped in with a seamless, digital visitor management system tailored for industrial environments. The system enabled OTP-based visitor verification, photo capture, real-time tracking, and instant access control — all through a simple, user-friendly interface. As a result, Easternbulk successfully secured its premises, maintained a verified record of every entry, and ensured that only authorized personnel could access its sensitive areas.', 'Used by Easternbulk Lime to connect production units, ensure real-time reporting, and coordinate effortlessly across departments — all while staying secure and efficient with Google Workspace and Onfra.', 'Easternbulk Lime modernized its industrial access and compliance checks by implementing Onfra’s secure facility automation tools.', 'Manufacturing Company', 'Tuticorin, TN', '100+', 'Visitor module', '1+ years');

